title: The Abduction (1960) Full Bonanza Western TV Episode

sources.title: The Abduction (1960) Full Bonanza Western TV Episode
sources.description:
Jennifer Beale is abducted in the hopes her rich father, Joshua, the richest silver baron on the Comstock, will pay a $1M ransom. The plan unravels when the beautiful Della is killed and Hercules, who loves her, finds out who did it.. Gerald Mohr and Stafford Repp guest star.
 
Director: Charles F. Haas
Writer: Herman Groves
Stars: Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker 
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
